name: Road to Mictlan - Vocho Lindo y Querido #1
description:
"Camino Al Mictlán", 3er Drop Colectivo de NFTianguis.

Artista: Natalie Larrodé

To commemorate the last Vocho produced worldwide on July 30th, 2003, at the plant of Puebla, Mexico, and to help us give a proper farewell, through the Mexican tradition of the Day of the Dead, to all the people, memories, and things lost in time.

The series “Vocho Lindo y Querido: a love story from 1967 to 2003” explores a cultural icon, the “Vocho” –or Volkswagen Sedan–, in the context of Mexicanness over the last five decades, through 36 NFTs on the Tezos Blockchain, one for each year the car was produced and sold in México. For more information, visit: https://natalielarrode.com/vocho-lindo-y-querido/

4096px X 4096px png by @natlarrode.
